author: antonio
msg: Improved dynamic selection list performance inside repeaters. Deprecate @dynamic in <fd:selection-list> in favor of @cache. Posible @cache values are: request, static, none. @cache='static' is equivalent to @dynamic='false'. @cache='none' is equivalent to @dynamic='true'. @cache='request' is new, similar to @dynamic='true' + caching the selection list per request.
